summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, amending Plat 36W, page 102 of the Official Land Use Map, to rezone approximately 1.15 acres of property located at 1100 Fairview Avenue North from Commercial 2 with a 65-foot height limit (C2/65') to Commercial 2 with an 85-foot height limit (C2/85'). Petition of Fred Hutchinson Cancer Research Center, C.F. 300315)
committee: Housing, Community Development and Urban Environment
